4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed to transform participants into cybersecurity specialists without prior experience. This 16-week program includes three live online classes weekly, with a maximum of 16 students per class. Students gain foundational knowledge in Windows, Linux, and server administration, along with practical skills in cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence. The bootcamp also covers risk management and compliance with international standards. Graduates receive a recognized official 4Geeks Completion Certificate. Classes are available in both English and Spanish. For more details, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop